glosses: To direct, to give direction, to turn.
To address a remark or question towards someone.

etymology: Inherited from Ottoman Turkish یونلتمك (yönültmek), equivalent to yön (“direction”) + -el (verb-forming suffix) + -t (causative voice) + -mek. Cognate with Uzbek yo'naltirmoq and Azerbaijani yönəltmək.
